race.comment: ONE BEAT NO BEAT (6) made progress last start to finish third over 1200m at Beaudesert after being in contention on the turn. Will be at peak fitness and has the talent to take care of this field. LADY ZAYDI (11) comes here off a last-start fifth, beaten 2 lengths, over 1300m at Toowoomba. Likely to feature in the finish. FIRE AND LIGHT (3) is back from a spell of five-and-a-half months. Scored a determined win at his final run last preparation at Gatton over 2000m. Sure to make his presence felt while fresh. GIDDAY GIDDAY (5) is coming off a last-start fourth, beaten 1.5 lengths, over 1300m at Toowoomba. Deserves serious consideration.
